<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-secondary-fixed">Those looking for 2-week quick fixes; this is a rigorous, senior-level program.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-xl opacity-60">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-error" data-icon="cancel">cancel</span>
<div>
